string.name: apiDocumentationLinks
string.comment:
%1$s links to a personal token app example (string: personalTokenAppExample).
%2$s links to the API documentation (string: apiDocumentation).
Full sentence after %1$s and %2$s have been substituted: "Here's a personal app token example and the API documentation."
personalTokenAppExample and apiDocumentation can both be translated separately.
